京报》将间接引导网暴的报道删除，仅留存一篇有利于刘学州的文章（[[今日头条|今日头条]]、[[百家号|百度百家号]]未删除<ref name=":4" /><ref>{{Cite web |author=新京报 |date=2022-01-19 |title=寻亲男孩刘学州生母谈拉黑隐情：想平静生活 |url=https://baijiahao.baidu.com/s?id=1722344331206255797 |website= |publisher=百度百家号 |access-date=2022-07-01 |archive-date=2022-07-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220701123749/https://wappass.baidu.com/static/captcha/tuxing.html?ak=572be823e2f50ea759a616c060d6b9f1&backurl=https%3A%2F%2Fmbd.baidu.com%2Fnewspage%2Fdata%2Flandingsuper%3Fthird%3Dbaijiahao%26baijiahao_id%3D1722344331206255797%26wfr%3D%26c_source%3Dduedge&timestamp=1656679067&signature=a7ef02e8eb385893ad22098f076fa584 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |author=新京报 |date=2022-01-20 |title=寻亲男孩刘学州将起诉生父母 舅妈：与同父弟弟比心里有落差 |url=https://baijiahao.baidu.com/s?id=1722438117903076558 |website=百度百家号 |access-date=2022-07-01 |archive-date=2022-07-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220701123750/https://wappass.baidu.com/static/captcha/tuxing.html?ak=572be823e2f50ea759a616c060d6b9f1&backurl=https%3A%2F%2Fmbd.baidu.com%2Fnewspage%2Fdata%2Flandingsuper%3Fthird%3Dbaijiahao%26baijiahao_id%3D1722438117903076558%26wfr%3D%26c_source%3Dduedge&timestamp=1656679069&signature=0b91c65eca4058f39060b2c10a0fa57b }}</ref><ref name=":5" />），并将另一则有关刘学州起诉的报道置顶一天，全部社交账号开启了精选评论模式，变相禁止网民评论。截至目前，《新京报》对此事仍无正面回应。

